    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a full VANOS refresh and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The chassis retains its signature balance thanks to a limited-slip differential and refreshed suspension geometry. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains robust with excellent throttle response and a linear power band. A true driver's car optimized for tactile feedback and high-RPM performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
