    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained 2019 Audi A6 3.0T Premium Plus in Mythos Black Metallic. This executive sedan offers a refined driving experience with its 335-hp turbocharged V6 and legendary Quattro all-wheel drive. The exterior remains striking, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger rim consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the Nougat Brown leather interior is in excellent shape, free of tears or odors, and features the dual-screen MMI touch response system and Bang & Olufsen 3D Premium sound. All electronics, including the Virtual Cockpit and ambient lighting, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is robust, with a documented service history, recent tire rotation, and fresh fluids. This is a reliable, high-spec vehicle ready for its next owner. Includes two key fobs and original owner's manuals.",
